-=[ Remote Deposit ]=-

These commands allow you access to the Mages Vault from a remote location.
The avaliable commands are:

- reposit <obj> - put item into the vault.
- redraw <obj>  - withdraw item from the vault.
- relist <str>  - list items within the vault.  <str> is optional
                  in case you want to specify type of items to list.

You cannot deposit/withdraw money remotely.

